For some reason all the parts in the VAB are duplicated. i Checked the gamedata folder and i dont see any duplicated files.

i just noticed that the spp parts arent duplicated though fixed it i deleted the parts folder inside squad and and started the patcher

Edited October 8, 2014 by natas
I also have this issue, but I don't know how to fix it, sorry

For any further discussions see here: http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/95820-Double-parts-%28with-fix%29
